The paper discusses the evolution of cellular networks and the design of future networks, which involves multiple objectives and tradeoffs between them. This suggests that the paper could belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), or Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper mentions the support for high data rates, which could relate to Multimedia (cs.MM) or Architecture (cs.AR) sub-categories. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.IT, cs.NI, and cs.SY, followed by cs.MM and cs.AR.
